visualization_settings.text: Dynamics Turnover, users, Revenue comparing periods

native.query:
WITH users AS (select USER_ID, min(CREATED_AT) as first_tr
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    where confirmed and TYPE_MAIN = 'buy'
    group by 1)
    select date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as dt
     , sum(case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) AS Turnover_EUR_new
     , sum(case when first_tr != TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) AS Turnover_EUR_old
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS 
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on TRANSACTIONS.SELECTIVE_FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.REGION_ID
    inner join users on users.user_id = TRANSACTIONS.user_id
where TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT >= '2021-01-01 00:00:00' and
      TYPE_MAIN = 'buy' and
      SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      confirmed and
      {{FIRST_PERIOD_TIME}} and
      {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and {{network}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
      {{pay_system}} and {{REGION}} and {{geo_card}} and {{card_country}} and {{acquirer_name}}
group by 1

card.name: Share user based Turnover First period time by wallet

native.query:
WITH users AS (select w.ADDRESS, min(tr.CREATED_AT) as first_tr
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS as tr
    inner join (select RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID, PARENT_ID from MART.TRANSACTIONS where CONFIRMED) as tr_w on tr_w.RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID = tr.ID
    inner join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WITHDRAWALS as w on tr_w.PARENT_ID = w.ID
    where tr.confirmed and tr.TYPE_MAIN = 'buy'
    group by 1)
select date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as dt
     , sum(case when TRANSACTIONS.USER_BASED_SELECTIVE then TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR end)/sum(TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR) AS Turnover_EUR
     , sum(case when TRANSACTIONS.USER_BASED_SELECTIVE and TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT = first_tr then TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR end)/
          sum(case when TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT = first_tr then TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR end) AS Turnover_EUR_only_new_users
      , sum(case when TRANSACTIONS.USER_BASED_SELECTIVE and TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT != first_tr then TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR end)/
          sum(case when TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT != first_tr then TRANSACTIONS.TURNOVER_EUR end) AS Turnover_EUR_only_old_users
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on TRANSACTIONS.SELECTIVE_FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.region_id
    inner join (select RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID, PARENT_ID from MART.TRANSACTIONS where CONFIRMED) as tr_w on tr_w.RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID = TRANSACTIONS.ID
    inner join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WITHDRAWALS as w on tr_w.PARENT_ID = w.ID
    inner join users on users.ADDRESS = w.ADDRESS
where TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT >= '2024-01-01 00:00:00' and
      TRANSACTIONS.TYPE_MAIN = 'buy' and
      TRANSACTIONS.SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      TRANSACTIONS.confirmed and
      {{FIRST_PERIOD_TIME}} and
      {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and {{network}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
      {{pay_system}} and {{REGION}} and {{geo_card}} and {{card_iso_country}} and {{acquirer_name}}
group by 1

card.name: Conversion rate from calculation first period

native.query:
WITH users AS (select USER_ID
              , coalesce(min(case when t_confirmed then CREATED_AT end), min(CREATED_AT)) as first_tr
    from MART.CALCULATIONS_UNIQ
    group by 1)
select date_trunc({{granularity}}, CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT) as dt
     , count(case when t_confirmed then 1 end)/count(1) as Conversion_rate
     , count(case when t_confirmed and CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT <= first_tr then 1 end)/count(case when CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT <= first_tr then 1 end) as Conversion_rate_new_users
     , count(case when t_confirmed and CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT > first_tr then 1 end)/count(case when CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT > first_tr then 1 end) as Conversion_rate_old_users
    from MART.CALCULATIONS_UNIQ 
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.region_id
    left join users on  users.user_id = CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.user_id
where CALCULATIONS_UNIQ.CREATED_AT >= '2024-01-01 00:00:00' and
      {{FIRST_PERIOD_TIME}} and
      {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
      {{pay_system_calc}} and {{REGION}} and {{geo_card}}
group by 1

native.query:
WITH users AS (select USER_ID, min(CREATED_AT) as first_tr
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    where confirmed and TYPE_MAIN = 'buy'
    group by 1),
    min_dt AS (select min(CREATED_AT) as min_dt
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    where {{CREATED_AT}})
    select tr.* from
(select date_trunc({{granularity}}, users.first_tr) as dt
     , count(distinct case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then users.USER_ID end) as count_users_all
     , count(case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TRANSACTIONS.ID end) as count_transactions
     , sum( case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) as Turnover_fisrt_tr
     , sum( case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then GMV_EUR end) as GMV_fisrt_tr

     , count(distinct case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then users.USER_ID end) as count_users_returned
     , count(distinct case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then users.USER_ID end)/nullifzero(count(distinct case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then users.USER_ID end)) as share_users_returned
     , count(case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TRANSACTIONS.ID end) as count_transactions
     , sum( case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) as Turnover_returned
     , sum( case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then GMV_EUR end) as GMV_returned

    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on TRANSACTIONS.SELECTIVE_FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.REGION_ID
    inner join users on users.USER_ID = TRANSACTIONS.user_id

where TYPE_MAIN = 'buy' and
      SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      confirmed and
      {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and {{network}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
      {{pay_system}} and {{REGION}} and {{geo_card}} and {{card_iso_country}} and {{acquirer_name}}
group by 1
order by 1) as TR
    inner join min_dt on 1=1
    where dt >= min_dt

native.query:
WITH us_tr AS (select USER_ID
                    , TRANSACTIONS.iD
                    , sum(TURNOVER_EUR) over (partition by USER_ID order by TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) AS TURN_user
                    , case when TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT = min(TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) over (partition by USER_ID) then 'new' else 'old' end type_user
               from MART.TRANSACTIONS
               left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on TRANSACTIONS.SELECTIVE_FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
               left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.region_id
               where TYPE_MAIN = 'buy'
                 and CONFIRMED
                 and {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
                 {{widget_id}} and {{network}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
                 {{pay_system}} and {{REGION}}  and {{card_geo}} and {{card_iso_country}} and {{acquirer_name}}
                 ),

     period_1 AS (WITH pre_dt AS (select USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                                       , IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                                       , CASE
                                             WHEN TURNOVER_EUR < 200 THEN 'less 200 EUR'
                                             WHEN TURNOVER_EUR < 700 THEN 'less 700 EUR'
                                             ELSE 'more 700 EUR' END                             AS SUM_TR
                                       , type_user
                                       , SUM(TURNOVER_EUR)                                       AS TURNOVER_EUR_1
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR)                                        AS REVENUE_EUR_1
                                       , SUM(GMV_EUR)                                            AS SUM_GMV_1
                                       , SUM(FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR)                              AS FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1
                                       , SUM(FEE_RATIO_RATES_FIAT_EUR)                           AS Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1
                                       , count(distinct us_tr.USER_ID)                           as count_users_1
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR) / SUM(TURNOVER_EUR)                    AS Rev_Turn_1
                                       , SUM(TURNOVER_EUR) / count(distinct to_date(CREATED_AT)) AS avg_day_TURN_1
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR) / count(distinct to_date(CREATED_AT))  AS avg_day_Rev_1
                                  from MART.TRANSACTIONS
                                           inner join us_tr on us_tr.id = TRANSACTIONS.id
                                  where {{fisrt_period_time}}
                                  group by 1, 2, 3, 4
                                  order by 1, 2, 3, 4),
                       pre_total AS (select SUM(TURNOVER_EUR_1)                      AS TURNOVER_EUR_1
                                          , SUM(REVENUE_EUR_1)                       AS REVENUE_EUR_1
                                          , SUM(SUM_GMV_1)                           AS SUM_GMV_1
                                          , SUM(FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1)             AS FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1
                                          , SUM(Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1)               AS Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1
                                          , sum(count_users_1)                       as count_users_1
                                          , SUM(REVENUE_EUR_1) / SUM(TURNOVER_EUR_1) AS Rev_Turn_1
                                          , avg(avg_day_TURN_1)                      AS avg_day_TURN_1
                                          , avg(avg_day_Rev_1)                       AS avg_day_Rev_1
                                     from pre_dt)

                  select 'Period 1'                                                 As Period
                       , cast(USER_BASED_SELECTIVE as varchar(10))                  AS USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                       , cast(IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC as varchar(10))                     AS IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                       , SUM_TR
                       , type_user
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_1
                       , REVENUE_EUR_1
                       , SUM_GMV_1
                       , FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1
                       , Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1
                       , count_users_1
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_1 / sum(TURNOVER_EUR_1) over (partition by 1) as share_turn_1
                       , Rev_Turn_1
                       , count_users_1 / sum(count_users_1) over (partition by 1)   as share_users_1
                       , avg_day_TURN_1
                       , avg_day_Rev_1
                  from pre_dt

                  union all
                  select 'Period 1' As Period
                       , 'Total'    AS USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                       , 'Total'    AS IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                       , 'Total'    AS SUM_TR
                       , 'Total'    AS type_user
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_1
                       , REVENUE_EUR_1
                       , SUM_GMV_1
                       , FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1
                       , Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1
                       , count_users_1
                       , 1          as share_turn_1
                       , Rev_Turn_1
                       , 1          as share_users_1
                       , avg_day_TURN_1
                       , avg_day_Rev_1
                  from pre_total),

     period_2 AS (WITH pre_dt AS (select USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                                       , IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                                       , CASE
                                             WHEN TURNOVER_EUR < 200 THEN 'less 200 EUR'
                                             WHEN TURNOVER_EUR < 700 THEN 'less 700 EUR'
                                             ELSE 'more 700 EUR' END                             AS SUM_TR
                                       , type_user
                                       , SUM(TURNOVER_EUR)                                       AS TURNOVER_EUR_2
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR)                                        AS REVENUE_EUR_2
                                       , SUM(GMV_EUR)                                            AS SUM_GMV_2
                                       , SUM(FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR)                              AS FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2
                                       , SUM(FEE_RATIO_RATES_FIAT_EUR)                           AS Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2
                                       , count(distinct us_tr.USER_ID)                           as count_users_2
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR) / SUM(TURNOVER_EUR)                    AS Rev_Turn_2
                                       , SUM(TURNOVER_EUR) / count(distinct to_date(CREATED_AT)) AS avg_day_TURN_2
                                       , SUM(REVENUE_EUR) / count(distinct to_date(CREATED_AT))  AS avg_day_Rev_2
                                  from MART.TRANSACTIONS
                                           inner join us_tr on us_tr.id = TRANSACTIONS.id
                                  where {{Second_period_time}}
                                  group by 1, 2, 3, 4
                                  order by 1, 2, 3, 4),
                       pre_total AS (select SUM(TURNOVER_EUR_2)                      AS TURNOVER_EUR_2
                                          , SUM(REVENUE_EUR_2)                       AS REVENUE_EUR_2
                                          , SUM(SUM_GMV_2)                           AS SUM_GMV_2
                                          , SUM(FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2)             AS FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2
                                          , SUM(Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2)               AS Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2
                                          , sum(count_users_2)                       as count_users_2
                                          , SUM(REVENUE_EUR_2) / SUM(TURNOVER_EUR_2) AS Rev_Turn_2
                                          , avg(avg_day_TURN_2)                      AS avg_day_TURN_2
                                          , avg(avg_day_Rev_2)                       AS avg_day_Rev_2
                                     from pre_dt)

                  select 'Period 2'                                                 As Period
                       , cast(USER_BASED_SELECTIVE as varchar(10))                  AS USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                       , cast(IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC as varchar(10))                     AS IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                       , SUM_TR
                       , type_user
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_2
                       , REVENUE_EUR_2
                       , SUM_GMV_2
                       , FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2
                       , Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2
                       , count_users_2
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_2 / sum(TURNOVER_EUR_2) over (partition by 1) as share_turn_2
                       , Rev_Turn_2
                       , count_users_2 / sum(count_users_2) over (partition by 1)   as share_users_2
                       , avg_day_TURN_2
                       , avg_day_Rev_2
                  from pre_dt

                  union all
                  select 'Period 2' As Period
                       , 'Total'    AS USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                       , 'Total'    AS IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                       , 'Total'    AS SUM_TR
                       , 'Total'    AS type_user
                       , TURNOVER_EUR_2
                       , REVENUE_EUR_2
                       , SUM_GMV_2
                       , FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2
                       , Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2
                       , count_users_2
                       , 1          as share_turn_2
                       , Rev_Turn_2
                       , 1          as share_users_2
                       , avg_day_TURN_2
                       , avg_day_Rev_2
                  from pre_total),
     change_row AS (select 'Change'                                          As Period
                         , 'Change'                                          AS USER_BASED_SELECTIVE
                         , 'Change'                                          AS IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                         , 'Change'                                          AS SUM_TR
                         , 'Change'                                          AS type_user
                         , TURNOVER_EUR_2 - TURNOVER_EUR_1                   AS TURNOVER_EUR_2
                         , REVENUE_EUR_2 - REVENUE_EUR_1                     AS REVENUE_EUR_2
                         , SUM_GMV_2 - SUM_GMV_1                             AS SUM_GMV_2
                         , FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2 - FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_1 AS FEE_MERCURIO_FIAT_EUR_2
                         , Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2 - Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_1     AS Mark_up_Revenue_EUR_2
                         , count_users_2 - count_users_1                     AS count_users_2
                         , 1                                                 as share_turn_2
                         , Rev_Turn_2 - Rev_Turn_1                           AS Rev_Turn_2
                         , 1                                                 as share_users_2
                         , avg_day_TURN_2 - avg_day_TURN_1                   AS avg_day_TURN_2
                         , avg_day_Rev_2 - avg_day_Rev_1                     AS avg_day_Rev_2
                    from period_1
                             inner join period_2 on period_1.IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC = period_2.IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC
                    where period_1.IS_FAST_TRACK_KYC = 'Total')


select *
from period_1
union all
select *
from period_2
union all
select *
from change_row

native.query:
WITH users AS (select w.ADDRESS, min(tr.CREATED_AT) as first_tr
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS as tr
    inner join MART.TRANSACTIONS as tr_w on tr_w.RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID = tr.ID
    inner join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WITHDRAWALS as w on tr_w.PARENT_ID = w.ID
    where tr.confirmed and tr.TYPE_MAIN = 'buy'
    group by 1)
select date_trunc({{granularity}}, TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT) as dt
     , count(distinct w.ADDRESS) as count_wallets
     , count(distinct case when TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT = first_tr then w.ADDRESS end)/count(distinct w.ADDRESS) as share_new_wallets
     , count(distinct case when TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT = first_tr then w.ADDRESS end) as count_new_wallets
    from MART.TRANSACTIONS

    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.region_id
    inner join (select RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID, PARENT_ID from MART.TRANSACTIONS where CONFIRMED) as tr_w on tr_w.RELATED_TRANSACTION_ID = TRANSACTIONS.ID
    inner join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WITHDRAWALS as w on tr_w.PARENT_ID = w.ID
    inner join users on users.ADDRESS = w.ADDRESS

    user_filtered as (select USER_ID, first_tr
    from users
    inner join min_dt on 1=1 
    where first_tr >= min_dt and
    first_tr < max_dt )
select count(distinct case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then user_filtered.USER_ID end) as count_users_all
     , count(case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TRANSACTIONS.ID end) as count_transactions
     , sum(case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) as Turnover_fisrt_tr
     , sum(case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then GMV_EUR end) as GMV_fisrt_tr

     , count(distinct case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then user_filtered.USER_ID end) as count_users_returned
     , count(distinct case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then user_filtered.USER_ID end)/nullifzero(count(distinct case when first_tr = TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then user_filtered.USER_ID end)) as share_users_returned
     , count(case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TRANSACTIONS.ID end) as count_transactions
     , sum(case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then TURNOVER_EUR end) as Turnover_returned
     , sum(case when first_tr < TRANSACTIONS.CREATED_AT then GMV_EUR end) as GMV_returned

    from MART.TRANSACTIONS
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES on TRANSACTIONS.SELECTIVE_FEE_ID = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.ID
    left join REPLICA.WEBAPP_REGIONS on WEBAPP_REGIONS.id = WEBAPP_WIDGET_SELECTIVE_FEES.REGION_ID
    inner join user_filtered on user_filtered.USER_ID = TRANSACTIONS.user_id

where TYPE_MAIN = 'buy' and
      SOURCE_MAIN = 'widget' and
      confirmed and
      {{FIAT_CURRENCY}} and {{CRYPTO_CURRENCY}} and {{partner_name}} and
      {{widget_id}} and {{network}} and {{is_fast_track}} and {{is_amout_based}} and
      {{pay_system}} and {{REGION}} and {{geo_card}} and {{card_iso_country}} and {{acquirer_name}}
